2. **End Value**: The end amount of Paid-in Capital is also 13,000,000.00 on the end date (2024-02-05), indicating no change in the capital contributed by shareholders during this period.

Thus, the initial and end values for the capital contributed by shareholders are both 13,000,000.00.
